result.name: wayra-unltd-final-dataset-may-2016
result.notes: The data shows incubator/venture level detail about the Wayra UnLtd incubator, funded through the Social Incubator Fund (SIF). The SIF is a £10m fund administered by the Big Lottery, which supports social incubators to help them provide investment and support to early stage social ventures in the UK. This data is has been submitted by Wayra UnLtd.

organization.name: wayra-unltd
organization.title: Wayra UnLtd
organization.description:
A new partnership between UnLtd, the world's largest supporter of social entrepreneurs, and Wayra, Telefonica's global tech start-up accelerator programme. 50% funded by the UK Government.

Wayra UnLtd will be the first Wayra Academy focused on start-ups that make a positive social impact. The Academy is based in London.
